description:
Pre-order now to get day one access to the Trooper Pack. Play as the soldiers of the Empire from Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, Solo: A Star Wars Story, and The Mandalorian. 
- Imperial Death Trooper 
- Incinerator Stormtrooper 
- Range Trooper 
- Imperial Shoretrooper 
- Mimban Stormtrooper
name: LEGO® Star Wars™: The Skywalker Saga Trooper Pack (Preorder)
